min days to make m bouquets
wrong condition check return (noOfBouquets==m)
right condition check return (noOfBouquet>=m)
testcase: 
[1000000000,1000000000] m=1 k=1
noOfBouquets = 2, m=1
return true
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

min capacity of truck to ship packages with in n days
tip - starting counting days from zero (helper function)


    public static boolean function(int cap,int[] weights,int days){
        int load =0,cnt=1;  //first day to load
        for(int x:weights){   //load packages to truck
            if(load + x <=cap) load = load  + x;
            else{
                cnt=cnt+1;      //take next day and then
                load=x;        //load
            }
        }
        return (cnt<=days);
    }
